S.FORM: I 1968 a miheca saka 10 folad saka 28 a romi'ad masofoc ci Juan Orlando Hernández, malamikomoday a tamdaw. O Sawara'an no kitakit no Honduras anini i ci Juan Orlando Hernández, patirengan a romi'ad i 2014 a miheca saka 1 folad saka 27 a romi'ad.
